metadata.name: 「 真紅の鬼」Crimson Demon
metadata.description:
Are you tired of this world? 
Is finding temporary happiness really satisfying? 

"Let's me show you a happier world than this place"
that the last scene you see before it is all different...

The illustration will appear in an illustration book distributed by FND Community's circle at Comiket in Tokyo on August 14 2022
